<plot>This entry in a series of Warner Brothers shorts under the collective title of "Technicolor Adventures" features actress Jean Parker and several models from the Conover agency. Miss Parker and the models try on a series of gowns by the country's leading dress designers, and the film ends with a show of newly-designed furs.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?190229</url></doc>
